description:
Christmas is just right around the corner, so let's experience some holiday cheer! An animated retelling of Charles Dickens' classic novel, A Christmas Carol... But BETTER! Courtesy of yours truly. (me)
Link to my Patreon if you wanna support me and my mission of bringing back Sonic Underground: https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
